https://issues.apache.org/jira/projects/IOTDB/issues/IOTDB-779

The server do not add "" for measurement anymore, users should add "" in measurement and it is the part of the measurement name. 

insert into root.turbine1.d1(timestamp,"s.3") values(1,2);
insert into root.turbine1.d1(timestamp,"s. 3") values(1,2);
insert into root.turbine1.d1(timestamp,"s 3") values(1,2);
insert into root.turbine1.d1(timestamp,"s ") values(1,2);

